::KitKat::

"As soon as the Alince ship lands, we attack it. It's easier to hit a 
sitting target that a moving one. Bot or ship. And as for your other 
question, How would you know if I had a clone or not?"

She then started to question which one of her troop was a spy for 
Megatron, she was undecided between DarkMouse and Nighteyes.  She 
knew the Fox wasn't just because he was silly enough to try to fight 
a wolf. Megatron would have informed his crew member of her modes. 

She thought it would be better to show him and Aracnia what she had.
"Megatron, you know your the hardest bot to give a gift to? I will 
not discuss any such topic in the open. If you wish to talk, we will 
have to go inside.Aracnia, please join us."  She motioned they go 
inside.
